title: file_exists()
brief: Test whether a given path exists.
seealso: is_directory, executable, is_maildir
version: 0.08
----

<p>This function tests whether the specified path exists.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre>
if ( file_exists( "/usr/bin/imapsync" ) ) then
   <a href="/lua/msg.html">msg</a>( "We have imapsync installed" )
end
</pre>
